    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Is Speechify free?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Speechify offers a free plan with basic voices and limited minutes. It's enough to test the tool, but the free plan has restrictions on premium voices and total minutes.</p>

    <h3>Is Speechify better than ElevenLabs?</h3>
    <p>For text-to-speech and audiobook creation, yes. Speechify is designed specifically for reading documents, articles, and books aloud. ElevenLabs is better for voice cloning and custom voice projects, but Speechify has better document support.</p>

    <h3>Can I clone my voice with Speechify?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Speechify's voice cloning feature lets you upload 3 minutes of audio to create a custom AI voice that reads any text in your voice. This is available on the Pro plan.</p>

    <h3>Does Speechify work with PDFs?</h3>
    <p>Yes. You can upload PDFs directly and Speechify will read them. For scanned PDFs, Speechify uses OCR to extract the text before reading it aloud.</p>

    <h3>Can I use Speechify offline?</h3>
    <p>Not on the web app, but yes on the mobile apps (iOS and Android). Download your documents or audiobooks to the app for offline listening.</p>

